               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gospel of John (fols. 3ra-92va)
 - Bǝsrāta Yoḥannǝs "Gospel of
                     John" (fols. 3ra-92ra)
 - Postscript (fols. 92ra-92va)
 II) Malkǝʾa
                     Māryām "Image of Mary" (fols. 92va-103va) (ChRep no. 91, GrohHymn 34)
                     
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- The list of the “tituli” of the Gospel is missing.</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
